title: The Danleers - One Summer Night (320)
description:
The Danleers - One Summer Night (320)

The Danleers were a 1950's vocal group best known for their single "One Summer Night" which made the top ten in 1958.  They also recorded other songs, venturing into doo wop, early R&B, and soul music, but were never able to produce another hit.
